<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Floovioo Blog | Updates & Engineering</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/style.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-off-white text-slate-600 font-sans antialiased selection:bg-brand-blue selection:text-white">

    <%- include('../partials/landing-nav') %>

    <main>
        <!-- Header -->
        <section class="bg-white pt-24 pb-12 border-b border-slate-100">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
                <div class="text-brand-blue font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-sm mb-4">Engineering & Product</div>
                <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-deep-ocean mb-6">Latest from the Team</h1>
                <p class="text-xl text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Updates on features, tutorials, and the future of document automation.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Blog List -->
        <section class="py-16">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-12">
                
                <!-- Article 1 -->
                <article class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
                    <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 aspect-video bg-slate-100 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
                        <!-- Placeholder Image -->
                        <div class="w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-300">
                             <svg class="w-12 h-12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">
                            <span class="text-brand-blue font-bold">Product Update</span>
                            <span>•</span>
                            <time>Jan 15, 2026</time>
                        </div>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-deep-ocean mb-3 hover:text-brand-blue transition-colors">
                            <a href="#">Introducing Floovioo Brand: Governance for your Documents</a>
                        </h2>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                            We've solved the "Frankenstein Document" problem by separating content from style. Learn how our new governance engine keeps your PDFs consistent.
                        </p>
                        <a href="#" class="text-brand-blue font-bold hover:underline">Read more &rarr;</a>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <hr class="border-slate-100">

                <!-- Article 2 -->
                <article class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
                    <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 aspect-video bg-slate-100 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
                         <div class="w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-50 to-emerald-50 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-300">
                             <svg class="w-12 h-12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.384-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">
                             <span class="text-teal-600 font-bold">Tutorial</span>
                            <span>•</span>
                            <time>Jan 02, 2026</time>
                        </div>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-deep-ocean mb-3 hover:text-brand-blue transition-colors">
                            <a href="#">Automating Invoice Generation with Stripe Webhooks</a>
                        </h2>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                            A step-by-step guide to listening for `invoice.payment_succeeded` events and generating a compliant PDF receipt in under 500ms.
                        </p>
                        <a href="#" class="text-brand-blue font-bold hover:underline">Read more &rarr;</a>
                    </div>
                </article>

                 <hr class="border-slate-100">

                 <!-- Article 3 -->
                <article class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
                    <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 aspect-video bg-slate-100 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
                         <div class="w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-50 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-300">
                             <svg class="w-12 h-12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">
                             <span class="text-indigo-600 font-bold">Engineering</span>
                            <span>•</span>
                            <time>Dec 20, 2025</time>
                        </div>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-deep-ocean mb-3 hover:text-brand-blue transition-colors">
                            <a href="#">Why we chose Puppeteer over HTML2Canvas</a>
                        </h2>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                            Client-side rendering wasn't cutting it for print-fidelity. Here is why we moved our entire rendering pipeline to headless Chrome.
                        </p>
                        <a href="#" class="text-brand-blue font-bold hover:underline">Read more &rarr;</a>
                    </div>
                </article>

            </div>
        </section>

    </main>

    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>

</body>
</html>
